//弱引用/强引用  可配对引用在外面用MPWeakSelf(self)，block用MPStrongSelf(self)  也可以单独引用在外面用MPWeakSelf(self) block里面用weakself

#define SUPWeakSelf(type)  __weak typeof(type) weak##type = type

